---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | Koby L.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">About Me</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
      <p class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        I am a curious developer and engineer who loves to figure out how things work. Whether it's writing clean software architecture or soldering wires for a new hardware prop, I enjoy the complete process of bringing an idea into reality.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-4 text-white">Hobbies & Interests</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-zinc-300 space-y-2 mb-8">
        <li>Building custom Lightsabers and cosplay props</li>
        <li>Engineering and iterating on the '4th of July Tube'</li>
        <li>Organizing the annual Ghetto Olympics</li>
        <li>Algorithmic Stock Market analysis and UI tooling</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed">
        I believe that the best way to learn is by building. This portfolio is a collection of my favorite projects, showing not just the final result, but the iterations and failures that led there.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
